Package gov.nist.secauto.metaschema.binding.model.annotations

Annotation Type MetaschemaField

  • @Documented
@Retention(RUNTIME)
@Target(TYPE)
public @interface MetaschemaField
    This annotation indicates that the target class represents a Metaschema field.

    • Optional Element Summary

      Optional Elements 
      Modifier and Type Optional Element Description
      AllowedValues[] allowedValues
      Get the allowed value constraints for this field.
      Expect[] expect
      Get the expect constraints for this field.
      IndexHasKey[] indexHasKey
      Get the index-has-key constraints for this field.
      boolean isCollapsible
      Defines if the annotated class representing a Metaschema Field is collapsible, meaning fields with the same set of flag/values can be combined together, with an array of values containing the combination of corresponding field values.
      Matches[] matches
      Get the matches constraints for this field.

    • Element Detail

      • isCollapsible

        boolean isCollapsible
        Defines if the annotated class representing a Metaschema Field is collapsible, meaning fields with the same set of flag/values can be combined together, with an array of values containing the combination of corresponding field values.

        For a Metaschema field to be collapsible, it must have flags, otherwise the collapsible status is ignored.

        Returns:
        true if the field is collapsible, or false otherwise
        Default:
        false

      • allowedValues

        AllowedValues[] allowedValues
        Get the allowed value constraints for this field.
        Returns:
        the allowed values or an empty array if no allowed values constraints are defined
        Default:
        {}

      • matches

        Matches[] matches
        Get the matches constraints for this field.
        Returns:
        the allowed values or an empty array if no allowed values constraints are defined
        Default:
        {}

      • indexHasKey

        IndexHasKey[] indexHasKey
        Get the index-has-key constraints for this field.
        Returns:
        the allowed values or an empty array if no allowed values constraints are defined
        Default:
        {}

      • expect

        Expect[] expect
        Get the expect constraints for this field.
        Returns:
        the expected constraints or an empty array if no expected constraints are defined
        Default:
        {}
